Features summary (what this app provides)

Create / edit / delete notes with title, tags, content

Autosave with debounce (saves changes automatically)

Local JSON persistence (file: ~/.notes_saver_data.json) using Gson

Note versioning (up to last 20 versions) and restore capability

Pin & star notes (pinned notes shown first)

Search by title, content, or tags (live filtering)

Export single note to .txt and import JSON with notes

Lightweight Markdown-style preview (headings, bold, italics, inline code) via WebView

Reminder scheduling that shows a popup at the scheduled time

Clean modern UI using JavaFX and CSS

Build & Run

Ensure JDK 17+ and JavaFX SDK (matching version) are available.

Using Maven (recommended): from project root run:

mvn clean javafx:run


Or import as Maven project into IntelliJ and run app.Main.

If running from IDE without Maven, set VM args:

--module-path /path/to/javafx-sdk/lib --add-modules javafx.controls,javafx.fxml

Notes, polishing & extensions (resume bullets)

Add rich-text editor (HTMLEditor) or Markdown library for full Markdown support.

Add encryption for private notes (AES with user password).

Sync/backup to cloud (Google Drive / Firebase).

Add tags auto-complete and tag management view.

Add multi-window or system tray for quick notes.

Add unit tests for NoteManager persistence using temp directories.

Add desktop notifications for reminders (System Tray integration).

















ðŸ“˜ PROJECT GUIDE â€” Notes Saver Pro (Advanced JavaFX Desktop Application)
1. ABSTRACT

Notes Saver Pro is an advanced JavaFX-based desktop application designed to create, edit, search, secure, and organize digital notes.
It provides enhanced features such as:

Rich Text Editor

Categories/Tags

Dark/Light Themes

PIN/Password Protected Notes

Auto-save & Auto-backup

Export notes as .txt or .pdf

Modern, animated UI

This project showcases strong knowledge of Java, JavaFX, Object-Oriented Programming, file handling, UI/UX development, and MVC architecture.

2. INTRODUCTION

Storing and organizing notes digitally has become essential for students and professionals.
Traditional notepad-like apps lack features like:

Searching

Categorizing

Security

Auto-saving

Dark mode

Notes Saver Pro solves these problems by offering a complete note-management system with a modern GUI and strong backend logic.

3. PROBLEM STATEMENT

Users face difficulty managing large numbers of notes due to:

No categorization

No search option

No modern UI

No backup

No security

4. OBJECTIVES

Create a user-friendly digital notes app

Enable add/edit/delete operations

Provide secure notes with password lock

Implement full-text search

Add categories, tags & sorting

Provide dark/light themes

Allow export & backup

Auto-save notes

5. EXISTING SYSTEM

Existing tools like Windows Notepad or basic editors lack:

UX

Security

Tagging features

Search

Export options

Auto-save

6. PROPOSED SYSTEM

Notes Saver Pro includes:

Interactive JavaFX UI

Rich Text Editing

Search & Filters

Local database using JSON/Files

Secure Notes (PIN protected)

Auto Backup System

Notification pop-ups

Custom Themes

